This extension, named “115 Cookie Manager”, is designed to manage cookies for the 115.com website. It provides the following functionalities:

Apply: Users can manually input their own cookie values in the provided text area and apply them to the website by clicking the “Apply” button. The page will automatically navigate to 115.com in current tab after the new cookies are set.
Save: Users can save the manually input cookie values for future use by clicking the “Save” button. The saved cookie values will be loaded automatically the next time the extension is opened.
Export: Users can export the currently saved cookie values to a JSON file by clicking the “Export” button.
Import: Users can import cookie values from a JSON file by clicking the “Import” button. The imported cookie values will be displayed in the text area immediately.
Please note that this extension does not collect or store any user information. All data related to the cookies are entered by the user and stored locally on the user’s device. The extension does not have any access to the user’s personal data unless explicitly provided by the user. The user’s privacy is our top priority.
